OL,3,CChris Froome 'extremely lucky' after
OL,4,Csuffering near-fatal injuries in bike
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,FChris Froome's wife has told ITV News
OL,8,Fhe is "extremely lucky" and "doing
OL,9,Fokay" after a life-threatening bike
OL,10,Fcrash left him with five broken ribs,
OL,11,Fa broken back and a tear to his heart.
OL,13,FMichelle Froome said the cyclist
OL,14,Fsuffered what is known as a traumatic
OL,15,Fpericardial rupture - a tear to the
OL,16,Fsac around the heart, an injury that
OL,17,Fonly usually occurs in high-speed
OL,18,Fmotorbike and car crashes.
