OL,4,Csuffering near-fatal injuries in bike
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,FThe wife of the four-time Tour de
OL,8,FFrance winner told ITV News he is
OL,9,Fcontinuing to recover at the Sainte-
OL,10,FAnne Military Hospital in Toulon.
OL,12,FShe said the hospital had "been
OL,13,Famazing" and was highly specialised in
OL,14,Fthoracic trauma.
OL,16,F"He's very lucky he went there," she
OL,17,Fsaid, adding that he's likely to be in
OL,18,Fhospital for "another week or so".
