OL,7,FThe British cyclist was on a training
OL,8,Fride on Wednesday when the accident
OL,9,Fhappened and was taken by helicopter
OL,10,Fto a hospital in Toulon on the French
OL,11,FRiviera.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,FFroome was "in good spirits" after
OL,19,Fundergoing surgery last week, his wife
OL,20,Fsaid.
