OL,3,CChris Froome 'extremely lucky' after
OL,4,Csuffering near-fatal injuries in bike
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,FThe cyclist and his family thanked
OL,8,Ffans, friends and the cycling
OL,9,Fcommunity for their concern and kind
OL,10,Fmessages after his crash.
OL,12,FThis is not the first time Froome has
OL,13,Frequired surgery following a cycling
OL,14,Faccident.
OL,16,FIn 2019, he said he was "lucky to be
OL,17,Fhere" after crashing at nearly 35mph
OL,18,Fduring his fourth-stage reconnaissance
OL,19,Fof the Criterium du Dauphine.
